window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They won't settle for mere victory.</b></p> <p><b>They want to exterminate us. Every last one of us.</b></p> <p>A surprise attack has sent the Star Alliance fleeing for its life. A remnant of a remnant, their meager fleet—all that remains alive—flees to what seems like a safe harbor: a forgotten backwater planet called Earth.</p> <p>Join ace fighter pilot Chase as he teams up with the modern-day militaries of Earth and fights the last battle for the universe.</p> <p><b>Sixty-five hours of space-opera goodness. Download the Universe in Flames Megabox today.</b></p>"; 
